sliding with a radically different ecosystemic awareness opens up potentials for bodying beyond current legal and political limits into enchantingly vibrant and ecosomatically alive futures.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aHuman bodyxSocial aspectszAfrica. 4aAliveness. 4aBody. 4aBusiness Ethics. 4aCultural Anthropology. 4aEcology. 4aEconomy. 4aEcosomatics. 4aEthnology. 4aFascia. 4aGabon. 4aSocial Relations. 4aSomatics. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAliveness.  aBody.  aBusiness Ethics.  aCultural Anthropology.  aEcology.  aEconomy.  aEcosomatics.  aEthnology.  aFascia.  aGabon.  aSocial Relations.  aSomatics.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021 Englishz978311075418608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2021z9783111025100oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2021z978311076731540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839460115?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839460115zOpen Access70423C